Title: Via Negativa
Plot: Working without Scully's input, Doggett and Skinner try to stop the mysterious murder spree of a drug-induced religious cult leader, and it becomes clear that the man can enter the dreams of the people he knows and can kill them in their sleep.
GuestStars: Keith Szarabajka, Grant Heslov, Wayne Alexander, Kevin McClatchy, Lawrence LeJohn, Wayne King, Christopher Jacobs, Mary Ostrow
